## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of social media's impact. The rapidly evolving nature of social media platforms means that new trends and effects may emerge that are not covered in this report. Additionally, individual experiences with social media can vary widely, and the impacts discussed may not apply universally. Further research is needed to explore the long-term effects of social media usage on different demographics.